# Netlify _redirects — subdomain asset + page routing
# Rules evaluated top-to-bottom; first match wins.

# ── Static assets: 302 redirect from subdomain → main domain CDN ─────────
# Status 200 proxy doesn't work cross-domain with Netlify SSR (the proxy
# fetches through the SSR function which returns HTML, not the actual file).
# 302 makes the browser fetch directly from adagi0.com where CDN has them.
https://*.adagi0.com/_astro/*        https://adagi0.com/_astro/:splat        302!
https://*.adagi0.com/Cards/*         https://adagi0.com/Cards/:splat         302!
https://*.adagi0.com/background/*    https://adagi0.com/background/:splat    302!
https://*.adagi0.com/uploads/*       https://adagi0.com/uploads/:splat       302!
https://*.adagi0.com/favicon.ico     https://adagi0.com/favicon.ico          302!
https://*.adagi0.com/favicon.svg     https://adagi0.com/favicon.svg          302!

# ── Subdomain page rewrites (200 keeps subdomain in the URL bar) ──────────
https://demo.adagi0.com/*            https://adagi0.com/Demos/:splat         200!
https://demos.adagi0.com/*           https://adagi0.com/Demos/:splat         200!
